{"tid":547202,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個提升工作效率嘅方法/嗜好/行為/習慣","createTime":"2018-02-01T08:17:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T14:12:47.000Z","uid":126603,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"b95dfd4efc3c879f03faa2ecba42e21457b7660c","tid":547202,"uid":126603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T08:17:47.000Z","msg":"如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講下點解噉做幫到你。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就嚟陷入workload 大爆炸嘅period<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nHelp!"},{"pid":"423593ab6b543f0dec9bd4252a1e155d6c5b981e","tid":547202,"uid":89953,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T10:00:11.000Z","msg":"早瞓教早起身"},{"pid":"825fa18f30c0f261a5afde10f81bf1d0323a208d","tid":547202,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"423593ab6b543f0dec9bd4252a1e155d6c5b981e","tid":547202,"uid":89953,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T10:00:11.000Z","msg":"早瞓教早起身"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T10:08:25.000Z","msg":"最 basic最重要"},{"pid":"b54a54aa6927d81aec6cc6c9a1a28f8314f1d1f7","tid":547202,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T10:09:38.000Z","msg":"getting thing done"},{"pid":"8f53638a3c9a0f26507d6c958ea6e3d02d0ec536","tid":547202,"uid":89953,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"825fa18f30c0f261a5afde10f81bf1d0323a208d","tid":547202,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"423593ab6b543f0dec9bd4252a1e155d6c5b981e","tid":547202,"uid":89953,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T10:00:11.000Z","msg":"早瞓教早起身"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T10:08:25.000Z","msg":"最 basic最重要"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T10:30:32.000Z","msg":"真係影響最大<br />\n然後做野之前都會擺定一壺熱茶係枱頭，特別係冬天。<br />\n每做到某個時間就會停低休息一下，休息一定要離開個位，可能食少少零食或者挨一下。<br />\n因為做野要長時間對住電腦，坐係度對得耐我會又攰又唔舒服，所以都慣咗咁嘅形式。"},{"pid":"5b10256f8a22c70b8f7ea0b9c6664292440410aa","tid":547202,"uid":135890,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T10:59:50.000Z","msg":"令自己憎工作表現最好嘅同事"},{"pid":"c13a1ea47d4d8d4e8a68bc44eacd0c9779d9079d","tid":547202,"uid":28195,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T11:21:09.000Z","msg":"將工作拆細，一舊舊完成，唔會無從入手，又做得準確"},{"pid":"27f09c89f37e8ee5341698c9bbe2fe04a1be274c","tid":547202,"uid":134474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5b10256f8a22c70b8f7ea0b9c6664292440410aa","tid":547202,"uid":135890,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T10:59:50.000Z","msg":"令自己憎工作表現最好嘅同事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T11:31:32.000Z","msg":"nn9但正確"},{"pid":"d1f00a0d3ee624c20217269d978e46cd3f7df1c5","tid":547202,"uid":134474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T11:31:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>令自己憎工作表現最好嘅同事</blockquote>on9但正確</blockquote>"},{"pid":"b22120099abd887b43020ccb38894b661f427d89","tid":547202,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T17:08:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e117b97b423cf7a0ad3ea1470716068096f283c6","tid":547202,"uid":27741,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T19:58:52.000Z","msg":"勁早天未光就起身食少少野之後沖涼 要確保沖完都未天光<br />\n我自己咁做會覺得自己好撚勤力 好享受嗰種好似全世界得我一個醒左嘅感覺 咁就好撚有動力"},{"pid":"c9ab80b0eac68d4e79d890f7c88188501a209fcd","tid":547202,"uid":72638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T20:00:03.000Z","msg":"咖啡因"},{"pid":"2fcbfb2d4d491e0e8277dbf89f0427c7ef4d5c81","tid":547202,"uid":140523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T20:31:10.000Z","msg":"執到啲野勁整齊"},{"pid":"4f72afa90f7a297e105f75d804fe7f0205f061d9","tid":547202,"uid":48964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T01:19:08.000Z","msg":"間中refresh下個腦，例如望遠處景色"},{"pid":"62454b453db264a1d1de68a790cb25113d96362d